def: To come to for the purpose of chastising, rewarding,comforting; to come upon with reward or retribution; to appear beforeor judge; as, to visit in mercy; to visit one in wrath.[God] hath visited and redeemed his people. Like i. 68.
A spider monkey (Ateles belzebuth) of Brazil.
To convert into something human or belonging to man; as, tohumanize vaccine lymph.
To place in a hive; to hive.

The theory that structural variations, characteristic ofspecies and genera, are produced in animals and plants by the directinfluence of physical environments, and esp., in the case of animals,by effort, or by use or disuse of certain organs.
Keel-shaped; having a longitudinal prominence on the back; as,a keeled leaf.
In the form of tendrils; -- applied especially to the spermaticand ovarian veins.
A biography written by the subject of it; memoirs of one's lifewritten by one's self.
One who practices double dealing; a deceitful, trickish person.L'Estrange.
A line connecting places on the earth having the same meanwinter temperature. Cf. Isothere.
